 Risks & Mitigations

 Risk: Markdown rendering performance on large content
 Mitigation: Implement caching by content hash, measure render time

 Risk: Breaking existing functionality (card dashboards)
 Mitigation: Complete replacement means clean break, no partial states

 Risk: Mobile layout complexity
 Mitigation: Preserve proven DaisyUI drawer pattern, test early

 Risk: Knowledge graph queries slow
 Mitigation: Single Cypher query for all nav data, add indexes

